<h3 id="2-lemon-balm-plant">2. Lemon Balm Plant</h3>
<ul>
  <li>A lemon balm plant is a lovely housewarming present since the new homeowner may put it in the garden and enjoy its beauty as well as a variety of home advantages. It wishes the new homeowner a happy and prosperous life in their new house, symbolically(Gaumond, 2021).</li>
</ul>

