<h3 id="3-oregano">3. Oregano</h3>
<ul>
  <li>Oregano is a great housewarming or hostess present since it may be planted near the house and receive the advantages(Gaumond, 2021).</li>
  <li>Although cut flowers can be used to add color, texture, and aroma to floral arrangements, it is not a frequent practice(Gaumond, 2021).</li>
</ul>

